### ==== IDENTITY API ====
# Docs: http://localhost:5000/scalar/v1
# Base routes:
#   /api/v1/admin/users          — user lifecycle (Admin)
#   /api/v1/admin/sessions       — token/session admin (Admin)
#   /api/v1/admin/access-reviews — QĐ742 periodic reviews (Admin)
#   /api/v1/delegations          — role delegation (Authenticated)
#   /api/v1/mfa                  — TOTP / email OTP (Authenticated)

# ── Users Admin ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List users (paged, optional filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List users filtered by tenant and search term
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users?tenantId={{tenantId}}&search=nguyen&isActive=true&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create user (admin-initiated registration)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Nguyen Van A",
  "email": "nguyenvana@test.vn",
  "password": "Test@Password123!",
  "departmentCode": "DEPT-01",
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

###

### Lock user account
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/lock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Unlock user account
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/unlock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Admin-initiated password reset (sends reset email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/users/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/reset-password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ── Sessions Admin ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List active sessions (all users)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/sessions/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List active sessions for a specific user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/sessions/active?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Revoke a single token by OpenIddict token ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/sessions/TOKEN_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Revoke all sessions for a user (force re-login on all devices)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/sessions/user/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ── Access Reviews (QĐ742) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List pending access reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/access-reviews/pending?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List pending reviews for a specific tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/access-reviews/pending?tenantId={{tenantId}}&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Approve access review (retain user's role)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/access-reviews/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Reject access review (mark role for revocation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/access-reviews/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ── Role Delegations ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List delegations (filter by delegatorId or delegateId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/delegations?activeOnly=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create role delegation (bounded time window)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/delegations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delegatorId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "delegateId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "validFrom": "2026-03-14T00:00:00Z",
  "validTo": "2026-03-21T00:00:00Z",
  "reason": "Annual leave coverage"
}

###

### Revoke delegation
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/delegations/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ── MFA ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Get TOTP setup URI (render as QR code in client)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/mfa/setup
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Verify TOTP code from authenticator app
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/mfa/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "123456"
}

###

### Send email OTP (enqueues Hangfire job)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/mfa/send-otp
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
